name: backend-architect
description: "Backend architecture patterns and systems design for 2026: API
  design (REST/GraphQL/gRPC/MCP), database architecture
  (PostgreSQL/MongoDB/Redis/vector DBs), microservices, event-driven
  architecture, CQRS, saga patterns, caching strategies, scalability, security,
  observability (eBPF/OpenTelemetry), and cloud-native architecture (serverless,
  Kubernetes, FinOps, DR/HA, IaC). Trigger when: designing APIs, database
  schemas, microservices, event-driven systems, planning backend scalability, or
  making cloud infrastructure decisions."
version: 1.2.0
emoji: 🛠️
